WEBVTT

00:07:57.049 --> 00:08:00.207
to sustain it, to protect it,

00:08:00.231 --> 00:08:03.146
is apparently worth nothing.

00:08:06.009 --> 00:08:10.830
Now, how and what can we do about this?

00:08:10.854 --> 00:08:13.752
Well, I wrote first about it 30 years ago.

00:08:14.387 --> 00:08:18.373
Then in 2008, after
the global financial crisis,

00:08:18.397 --> 00:08:20.290
President Sarkozy of France

00:08:20.314 --> 00:08:24.697
asked three men who had all
won Nobel Prizes in Economics --

00:08:24.721 --> 00:08:27.675
Sen, Fitoussi and Stiglitz --

00:08:27.699 --> 00:08:29.621
to discover what I'd written about

00:08:29.645 --> 00:08:31.132
30 years ago.